DEL
    delete selected
BACKSPACE
    open parent folder
LEFT, RIGHT, END, HOME
    navigate list
F2
    start rename
MOUSE DOWN 
    on item
        select item
    on list anywhere
        activates list
    outside of list
        deactivates list
    when renaming, outside of textarea
        finish rename
DOUBLE CLICK
    on file
        open file in new tab
    on folder
        open folder
ENTER - simulate doubleclick
DRAG
    to list
        upload file(s)
CTRL+A
    select all

